t:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.22222em;\">V</span></span></span></span></span> 都满足，我们可以取特定的 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>α</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\alpha</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.0037em;\">α</span></span></span></span></span> 来得到想要的结果。</p></div></details></p>\n<p><details  class=\"callout callout-type-quote\"><summary>答案</summary><div><p>\n<img src=\"https://static.memset0.cn/img/v6/2024/02/08/qx62KvQ0.png\"alt=\"\" ></p></div></details></p>\n<h2 id=\"4-正交矩阵相关概念\" style=\"position:relative;\">4. 正交矩阵相关概念<a href=\"#4-%E6%AD%A3%E4%BA%A4%E7%9F%A9%E9%98%B5%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5\" aria-label=\"4 正交矩阵相关概念 permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.memset0.cn/img/v6/2024/02/08/F1BvOHzs.png\"alt=\"\" ></p>\n<p><details  class=\"callout callout-type-quote\"><summary>答案</summary><div><p>\nBC</p></div></details></p>\n<h2 id=\"5-核空间与像空间\" style=\"position:relative;\">5. 核空间与像空间<a href=\"#5-%E6%A0%B8%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E4%B8%8E%E5%83%8F%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4\" aria-label=\"5 核空间与像空间 permalink\" class=\"an